response.original_title: National Parks Exploration Series: An Eagles View
response.overview: Prepare to take flight and explore America's greatest treasures in this birds-eye view exploration through our historic National Parks.  This breathtaking series journeys through the elegant and adventurous landscapes of our nation's most colorful and sacred places.  Each one unique, dramatic and powerful, our National Parks reveal the true heart and character of our great continent.  From the towering snowcapped mountains of Glacier to the small wildflowers of Yellowstone the paradise of Mother Nature's wilderness comes to you through hi-def imagery.  Witness the gripping history and majestic beauty of Yellowstone, The Great Smoky Mountains, The Everglades, the Grand Canyon, Yosemite, and many more through the unique perspective of - An Eagle's View!
